      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779473231704,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements\n- identify users by id, IP or api key\n- limit requests based on configurable rules\n- return proper error headers and status codes\n\n\nNon-functional requirements\n- availability >> consistency\n- low latency rate limit checks (<10ms)\n- Scalability: 1M rps, 100M DAU\n\nCore Entities\n- Request \n- Client (IP, userId, Api key)\n- Rules (100 r/s)\n\nSystem Interface\nisRequestAllowed(clientId, rulesId) -> {passes: boolean, remaining: number, resetTime: timestamp}",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements\n- identify users by id, IP or api key\n- limit requests based on configurable rules\n- return proper error headers and status codes\n\n\nNon-functional requirements\n- availability >> consistency\n- low latency rate limit checks (<10ms)\n- Scalability: 1M rps, 100M DAU\n\nCore Entities\n- Request \n- Client (IP, userId, Api key)\n- Rules (100 r/s)\n\nSystem Interface\nisRequestAllowed(clientId, rulesId) -> {passes: boolean, remaining: number, resetTime: timestamp}",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
